quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  16,90,"Tabitii Alla yamirii nunЙ—al, e moЖҙЖҙingol, e moЖҙЖҙagol e joomiraaЙ“e Й“adondiral. Himo haЙ—a gaay e pan-kare, e ko aГұinii, e bewre. Himo waajoo on, belajo'o, on waajitoray"
  16,91,"Hunnee ahadi Alla ndin si on ahodaama, wata on firtu goondooje Й—en Й“aawo Й—e tenntineede, gomЙ—ii on waЙ—ii Alla seedaniiЙ—o [on e hunnugol ngol]. Pellet, ko annduЙ—o ko golloton"
  16,92,"Wata on wonu wa on (debbo) firtunooЙ—o mottawol mun Й“aawo doole firtude, hiЙ—on jogitora goondooje mon Й—en janfondiro hakkunde mon, nde mofte [mon Й—en] wonata Й“urde tonaade e dii mofte goo. Anndee Alla no jarribora on Й—um. Ma O Й“anngina- na on Г‘alnde Darngal, kon ko luutondiraynoЙ—on e mun"
  16,93,"Sinno Alla muuyuno, O waЙ—ayno on mofte goote. Kono, Himo majjina on Mo O muuyi, O fewna on Mo O muuyi. Ma on lannditoye e kon ko gollaynoЙ—on"
  16,94,"Wata on jogitor goondooje mon janfondiro hakkunde mon, sakko koyngal [mon] mortotoo (fergito) Й“aawo ngal tabitude, meeЙ—iron bone sabu ko sakkiЙ—on kon e laawol Alla ngol. Hino woodani on lepte mawЙ—e"
  16,95,"Wata on waЙ—titir ahadi Alla ndin coggu fanЙ—ungu. Anndee ko ko woni ka Alla kon Й“uri moЖҙЖҙannde on, si tawno hiЙ—on anndi"
  16,96,"Ko marЙ—on kon re'ay (lanna), ko woni ka Alla kon ko heddotooЙ—um. Ma Men warjor Й“en muГұГұiiЙ“e njoЙ“di maЙ“Й“e ndin ko Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude e ko Й“e gollaynoo kon"
  16,97,"Kala golluЙ—o moЖҙЖҙere, woni gorko maa debbo, hara ko o gomЙ—inЙ—o, Ma Men wuurnu mo nguur- ndam laaЙ“uЙ—am. Ma Men warjor Й“e njoЙ“di maЙ“Й“e ndin, ko Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude e ko Й“e gollaynoo kon"
  16,98,"Si a janngay Alqur'aana, moolor Alla seytaane raЙ—aaЙ—o on"
  16,99,"Kanko on, mbawdi(cemmbe) alanaa mo e Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e, Й“e fawii e hoore Joomi maЙ“Й“e"
  16,100,"Anndee mbawdi makko ndin, ko hoore Й“en welduЙ“e e makko woni, e Й“en sirkirooЙ“e sabu makko"